data.description: Top Floor condo in attractive courtyard building with lovely tree-top view of Clyde-Brummel Playground. As you enter, the foyer with roomy closet - nice size bath, and galley kitchen with Italian maple cabinets, window and counter seating make this layout easy to live in. There's bonus storage right downstairs.   Additional highlights of this remarkable condo include hardwood floors throughout, in-unit laundry, and an abundance of closet space for all your storage needs. The building also offers a common outdoor area, perfect for enjoying the fresh air and soaking up the sunshine. Short distance to: Peckish Pig, Sweet Temptations, Cafe Coralie, North Shore Cider, and the red/purple/yellow CTA lines. FHA Approved.  Tons of street parking and a permit city lot right across the street.
